{"tid":834890,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【🌋樓爆2018】業主第一滴血😂低市價一成求售向上蝕312萬","createTime":"2018-09-24T12:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T09:44:03.000Z","uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f41a97bc1d0b6212f7d483fa3f81ef2db7fd062e","tid":834890,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:41:43.000Z","msg":"美聯物業梁兆堅表示，沙田中心本月暫錄約2宗成交，其中廣寧大廈低層A室，2房間隔，向東南望內園景，實用面積288方呎，放盤近半年，買家心儀上址附有簡約裝修，睇樓3次後拆槌成交，成交價528萬元，呎價18,333元，低市價一成。資料顯示，屋苑同面積的海寧大廈高層A室，今年7月以590萬元成交，呎價20,486元。<br />\n<br />\n原業主2011年2月以215.6萬元購入物業，是次轉售賬面獲利312.4萬元，升值逾1.4倍。<br />\n<br />\n記者:朱連峰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180923/58714988\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180923%2F58714988&d=PfME75FzGX8h9tP9z3Zjni7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=3e91611b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180923%2F58714988&h=bc217426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180923/58714988</a>"},{"pid":"b7f8e6d37b1df110b88ab33162b52c35b759b6cb","tid":834890,"uid":41157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:45:15.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f65cc3215b4665d9a38e1ef9e77d2ed672b2b3d","tid":834890,"uid":92127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:46:37.000Z","msg":"新界唔計"},{"pid":"0e74cd3a5d3c0a54e94c50551a86a20ada160e38","tid":834890,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7f8e6d37b1df110b88ab33162b52c35b759b6cb","tid":834890,"uid":41157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:45:15.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T12:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src